Name: Good Hell
About the game: You will live the terrible experience of a camera with two arms ready to dodge red balls, not to fall on the toxic cloud and not to be demoralized by a god who cares about you. Gameplay:You move fast, you can jump on walls and you can use the dash to reach other places. By changing levels you will get the chance to do a loaded jump and an ultra fast slide. Finally you will have the coolest weapon ever ......THE RAMPINO -Be prepared to jump in the right way and at the right time. -A Jumping on the walls with grace and ferocity. -Learn to use the dash sparingly and quickly. -Use everything you have available to complete the level and boast it with your friends. -Use the grapple smartly and quickly. -There is no SAVE in this game. -Each round a different music. -At the end of the level you have immense satisfaction in taking the BANANA -Very difficult, not for the faint of heart but doable
